Title: Fix exception 'format' on RRD creation of you have created RRD rules with the previous version
Level: 2
Edition: cee
Component: metrics
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1457422151

If you had created some rules for RRD configuration of hosts or services
then you would run into an exception with missing <tt>'format'</tt>. This
has been fixed.
